    "history" -> {"13.1", "14.2", "", ""}, "context" -> "QuantumMob`Q3`", 
    "keywords" -> {"symmetric group"}, "specialkeywords" -> {}, 
    "tutorialcollectionlinks" -> {}, "index" -> True, "label" -> 
    "Quantum Mob/ Q3 Symbol", "language" -> "en", "paclet" -> "QuantumMob/Q3",
     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "YoungNormalRepresentation[shape] calculates Young's normal \
representation of the symmetric group, and returns an full object \
YoungNormalRepresentation[shape, array]. YoungNormalRepresentation[shape, \
array] represents Young's normal representation of the symmetric group \
associated with integer partition shape and with matrices of adjacent \
transpositions stored in array. YoungNormalRepresentation[shape, array][prm] \
returns the matrix of permutation prm in Young's normal representation. \
YoungNormalRepresentation[n] returns the list of all irreducible \
representations of the symmetric group of degree n.", "synonyms" -> {}, 
    "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "YoungNormalRepresentation", 
    "titlemodifier" -> "", "metadescription" -> "", "windowtitle" -> 
    "YoungNormalRepresentation", "type" -> "Symbol", "uri" -> 
